data.description: If you are looking for the home of your dreams, then look no further. This spectacular 3,051 sq. ft. home offers a mix of lavish living and a natural outdoor view that will leave you breathless. Once inside, the high ceilings and the welcoming design offers a splash of comfort and elegance. The main level features a delightful eat-in kitchen, complete with a center island, and pantry. The first floor includes a laundry room, formal dining room, living room, office space, a half bathroom, and family room. Take a walk upstairs and you will find four spacious bedrooms, including a large master bedroom complete with an en suite bath and a generous walk-in closet. But Wait...THERE'S MORE! The full basement is a canvas with endless possibilities. Take your vision anywhere from a home theater, a home gym, or a playroom for the little ones. This space is a blank canvas for your creative dreams. The home doesn't stop there; the 6-foot-fenced backyard is immense and perfect for entertaining or relaxing. Featuring an above ground pool and patio. The early morning view is breathtaking. Don't let this dream home with tons of potential get away!
